# Observability: Actuator and Micrometer

**Actuator** surfaces operational endpoints; **Micrometer** bridges metrics to backends like Prometheus.

Lock down sensitive endpoints; pair metrics with **structured logging** and **distributed tracing** IDs.
@quiz: Which starter adds Spring Boot operational endpoints?
@option: spring-boot-starter-json
@correct: spring-boot-starter-actuator
@option: spring-boot-starter-aop
